\c 7
\s Isivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu loDavida
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi lapho inkosi yayihlezi endlini yayo, leN\nd kosi\nd* isiyiphumuzile inhlangothi zonke ezitheni zayo zonke\x + 1 Lan. 17.1-27.\x*,
\v 2 inkosi yathi kuNathani umprofethi\x + 7.17. 12.1.\x*: Akubone, mina ngihlala endlini yemisedari\x + 5.11.\x*, kodwa umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu uhlala phakathi kwamakhetheni\x + Eks. 26.1. Seb. 7.46.\x*.
\v 3 UNathani wasesithi enkosini: Hamba wenze konke okusenhliziyweni yakho, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ilawe\x + 1 Kho. 8.17,18. 1 Lan. 22.7. 28.2.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Kodwa kwathi ngalobobusuku, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kuNathani lisithi:
\v 5 Hamba uthi encekwini yami, kuDavida: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Wena uzangakhela yini indlu ukuze ngihlale \add kiyo\x + 1 Kho. 5.3. 8.19. 1 Lan. 22.8. 28.3.\x*\add*?
\v 6 Ngoba kangizange ngihlale endlini kusukela osukwini engenyusa ngalo abantwana bakoIsrayeli eGibhithe kuze kube lamuhla\x + 1 Kho. 8.16.\x*, kodwa bengihamba ethenteni lethabhanekeleni\x + 11.11. Eks. 40.18,19,34.\x*.
\v 7 Kuzo zonke \add izindawo\add* engihambe kuzo labo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli, ngake ngakhuluma ilizwi yini kwesinye sezizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + Levi 26.11,12. Dute. 23.14.\x*, engasilaya ukwelusa abantu bami uIsrayeli ngisithi\x + 5.2.\x*: Kungani lingangakhelanga indlu yemisedari?
\v 8 Ngakho-ke uzakutsho njalo encekwini yami, kuDavida, \add uthi\add*: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla: Mina ngakuthatha\x + 1 Sam. 16.11.\x* esibayeni sezimvu, ekulandeleni izimvu, ukuba ngumbusi phezu kwabantu bami, phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + Isa. 65.10. Hez. 25.5.\x*;
\v 9 ngangilawe loba ngaphi lapho oya khona, ngaquma zonke izitha zakho ngaphambi kwakho\x + 5.10. 8.6,14. 1 Sam. 18.14.\x*; ngakwenzela ibizo elikhulu njengebizo labakhulu abasemhlabeni\x + Gen. 12.2.\x*.
\v 10 Njalo ngizabamisela indawo abantu bami uIsrayeli, ngibagxumeke ukuze bahlale endaweni yabo\x + Hlab. 44.2. 80.8. Jer. 24.6. Amos 9.15.\x*, bangabe besanyikinyeka\x + 2 Kho. 21.8.\x*; labantwana benkohlakalo kabasayikubahlupha, njengakuqala,
\v 11 njalo kusukela osukwini engalaya ngalo abahluleli phezu kwabantu bami uIsrayeli\x + Hlu. 2.14,15,16. 1 Sam. 12.9,11. Hlab. 106.41,42.\x*; ngikuphumuze ezitheni zakho zonke\x + 7.1.\x*. Futhi iN\nd kosi\nd* iyakutshela ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenzela indlu\x + 7.27. Eks. 1.21. 1 Kho. 11.38. 1 Sam. 2.35.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Lapho insuku zakho sezigcwalisekile\x + 1 Kho. 2.1.\x*, usulele laboyihlo\x + Dute. 31.16. 1 Kho. 1.21. 2.10. Seb. 13.36.\x*, ngizamisa inzalo yakho emva kwakho, ezaphuma emibilini yakho, ngiqinise umbuso wayo\x + 1 Kho. 8.20. Hlab. 132.11.\x*.
\v 13 Yona izakwakhela ibizo lami indlu\x + 1 Kho. 5.5. 6.12. 8.19. 1 Lan. 22.10. 28.6.\x*; njalo ngizaqinisa isihlalo sobukhosi sombuso wayo kuze kube nininini\x + 7.16. Hlab. 89.4,29,36,37.\x*.
\v 14 Mina ngizakuba nguyise, layo ibe yindodana yami\x + Hlab. 89.26,27,30-33. Heb. 1.5.\x*; ezakuthi uba isenza okubi, ngizayijezisa ngentonga yabantu, langemivimvinya yabantwana babantu\x + 19.19. 24.17. 1 Kho. 8.47. 2 Lan. 6.37. Hlab. 106.6. Jer. 9.5.\x*.
\v 15 Kodwa umusa wami kawuyikusuka kiyo njengalokho nga\add wu\add*susa kuSawuli engamsusa ngaphambi kwakho\x + 1 Sam. 15.23,28. 1 Kho. 11.13,34.\x*.
\v 16 Lendlu yakho lombuso wakho kuzaqiniswa kuze kube nininini phambi kwami; isihlalo sakho sobukhosi sizaqiniswa kuze kube nininini\x + 7.13. Luka 1.33.\x*.
\v 17 Njengokwalamazwi wonke lanjengokwalo wonke lo umbono, ngokunjalo uNathani wakhuluma kuDavida\x + 7.4. Isa. 22.1,5.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Yasingena inkosi uDavida, yahlala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, yathi: Ngingubani mina, Nkosi Jehova, lendlu yami iyini, ukuthi ungifikise kuze kube lapha\x + Gen. 32.10.\x*?
\v 19 Kanti lokhu kusekuncinyane emehlweni akho, Nkosi Jehova; usukhulumile futhi ngendlu yenceku yakho ngokwesikhathi esikhatshana; lalokhu yindlela yabantu, Nkosi Jehova\x + Isa. 55.8.\x*.
\v 20 Pho, uDavida angabe esengezelela ngokuthini kuwe? Ngoba wena uyayazi inceku yakho, Nkosi Jehova\x + Hlab. 139.1-4.\x*.
\v 21 Ngenxa yelizwi lakho lanjengokwenhliziyo yakho wenzile zonke lezizinto ezinkulu ukuze uzazise inceku yakho.
\v 22 Ngakho umkhulu, Nkosi Jehova\x + 1 Lan. 16.25. 2 Lan. 2.5. Hlab. 48.1. 86.10. 96.4. 135.5. 145.3. Jer. 10.6.\x*; ngoba kakho onjengawe, njalo kakho uNkulunkulu ngaphandle kwakho\x + Eks. 15.11. Isa. 45.5.\x*, njengakho konke esikuzwileyo ngendlebe zethu.
\v 23 Yisiphi-ke isizwe esisodwa emhlabeni esinjengabantu bakho, njengoIsrayeli, uNkulunkulu owaya ukuzihlengela sona ukuba ngabantu\x + Dute. 4.7,32,34. 33.29. Hlab. 147.20.\x*, njalo wazenzela ibizo, walenzela izinto ezinkulu lezesabekayo\x + Dute. 10.21.\x*, kusenzelwa ilizwe lakho, phambi kwabantu bakho, owazihlengela bona eGibhithe, \add e\add*zizwe\add ni\add* la\add ku\add*bonkulunkulu bazo\x + Dute. 9.26. Neh. 1.10.\x*?
\v 24 Wasuziqinisela abantu bakho uIsrayeli ukuze babe ngabantu kuwe kuze kube nininini; lawe N\nd kosi\nd* usube nguNkulunkulu wabo\x + 7.13,16,26. Dute. 26.18.\x*.
\v 25 Khathesi-ke, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu, ilizwi olikhulume ngenceku yakho langendlu yayo liqinise kuze kube nininini, wenze njengokukhuluma kwakho\x + 1 Sam. 1.23. 1 Kho. 2.4.\x*.
\v 26 Njalo kalibe likhulu ibizo lakho kuze kube nininini, kuthiwe: IN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla inguNkulunkulu phezu kukaIsrayeli; lendlu yenceku yakho uDavida imiswe phambi kwakho.
\v 27 Ngoba wena, N\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, Nkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, wembule \add e\add*ndlebe\add ni\add* yenceku yakho, usithi: Ngizakwakhela indlu. Ngakho inceku yakho ithole enhliziyweni yayo ukuthi ikhuleke lumkhuleko kuwe\x + Joha. 17.17.\x*.
\v 28 Khathesi-ke, Nkosi Jehova, wena ungulowoNkulunkulu, lamazwi akho aliqiniso; ukhulume encekwini yakho lokhu okuhle.
\v 29 Ngakho-ke akuvume ubusise indlu yenceku yakho ukuze ibe phambi kwakho kuze kube nininini; ngoba wena, Nkosi Jehova, ukhulumile; langesibusiso sakho indlu yenceku yakho izabusiswa kuze kube nininini\x + 22.51. 7.13,16. 1 Sam. 1.22.\x*.